Interface StudentOrder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StudentByPriorityRequestDate, StudentByRequestDate, StudentChoiceOrder, StudentChoiceRealFirstOrder, StudentGroupsChoiceRealFirstOrder, StudentMajorOrder, StudentRandomOrder, StudentRandomRealFirstOrder

    public interface StudentOrder
